Record blackbox data

Usage: wheelctl diag record [OPTIONS] <DEVICE>

Arguments:
  <DEVICE>  Device ID or name

Options:
  -d, --duration <DURATION>  Recording duration in seconds [default: 120]
      --json                 Output in JSON format for machine parsing
  -o, --output <OUTPUT>      Output file path
  -v, --verbose...           Verbose logging
  -h, --help                 Print help
